creator: KJGamess
descriptionHtml:
Get ready for an epic adventure in my auto battler roguelike game! In this game, you'll lead a team of heroes on a journey through procedurally generated dungeons filled with dangerous enemies and valuable treasures. With a unique combination of tactical combat and randomized items, you'll need to strategize your way through each encounter, choosing the right heroes and abilities to take down your opponents.

As you progress through the game, you'll encounter new heroes with unique abilities, each with their own strengths and weaknesses. Your goal is tactical decision-making and adapting to the challenges presented by each dungeon.

But be warned - death is permanent in this roguelike adventure. Every defeat will send you back to the beginning, with a new set of challenges to face.

With a beautiful and immersive world, challenging gameplay, and endless replayability, my auto battler roguelike game will keep you coming back for more. Are you ready to embark on the ultimate adventure?"
descriptionShort: Roguelike auto battler with deep customization

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Items: Upgrade level is now capped at 10.
- Goblin Cleaver: Attack speed bonus is capped at 100.
- Fixed a bug that caused abilities to stop being cast.
- Critical hit runes no longer proc themselves.
- Buff effects should now apply correctly.
- Items modified by encounters should now apply stats correctly.
- Fixed various bugs related to the save system.
- Fixed thorns keepsakes.
- Multiple visual and UI issues have been resolved.
- Potential fixes applied to leaderboards.
